# 📄 Contract Review Tool

AI-powered contract analysis in 2 minutes. Upload any business contract and get instant insights on risks, terms, and negotiation points.

## 🚀 Quick Start

### 1. Set Your API Key (Required)

```bash
export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY='your-api-key-here'
```

To get an API key:
1. Go to https://console.anthropic.com/
2. Sign up or log in
3. Create an API key
4. Copy and paste it into the command above

### 2. Start the Server

```bash
./start_server.sh
```

Or manually:

```bash
python app.py
```

### 3. Open Your Browser

Go to: http://localhost:5000

