## 🔒 Security & Privacy

- **No Storage**: Contracts are processed in memory and immediately deleted
- **HTTPS Ready**: Enable SSL for production deployments
- **Environment Variables**: API keys stored securely in environment, not code
- **Minimal Logging**: Only errors are logged, no contract content

